      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! I'm finally parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it\u2019s a bittersweet day. This beauty has been my weekend baby\u2014always tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed with the good stuff. It\u2019s honestly like stepping back onto the showroom floor; the paint has that deep, mirror-like glow and the interior is so crisp it still feels fresh. It drives tight, smooth, and exactly how you'd hope. I\u2019ve obsessed over every detail so you can just turn the key and enjoy the ride. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate just how special this one is. Come on over, let's grab a coffee and talk cars!",
